Description
Hand-picked reads from the Amazon Charts: Most Read. For anyone looking for a good book to read on your couch or the subway, this list is a good place to start your search.
List:

The Outsider by Stephen King
The President Is Missing by Bill Blinton & James Patterson
Harry Potter and the Sorcerer’s Stone by J. Rowling
The Handmaid’s Tale by Margaret Atwood
Something in the Water by Catherine Steadman
The Woman in the Window by A. Finn
Little Fires Everywhere by Celeste Ng
The Fallen by David Baldacci
Ready Player One by Ernest Cline
The Great Alone by Kristin Hannah
